---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Off-Grid Living | Sunshine Tiny Houses"
  description="Go off-grid with solar power, composting toilets, rainwater harvesting and greywater solutions for self-sufficient tiny house living."
  canonical="https://www.sunshinetinyhouses.com.au/off-grid/"
>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Off-Grid Living</p>
      <h1>Sustainable Off-Grid Solutions</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__sub">Live independently, reduce your footprint, and cut your living costs — all in a beautifully built tiny home.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container og-intro">
      <h2>Self-Sufficient Living, Built Into Your Home</h2>
      <p>At Sunshine Tiny Houses, sustainability is at the heart of what we do. We offer comprehensive off-grid solutions for those seeking to reduce their environmental footprint and living expenses. Whether you want a fully independent home or simply want to reduce reliance on the grid, we can design and install the systems you need.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--surface">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our Off-Grid Options</p>
      <h2>What We Offer</h2>
      <div class="og-systems">

        <div class="og-card">
          <div class="og-card__icon">&#x2600;&#xFE0F;</div>
          <h3>Solar Power</h3>
          <p>We design and install advanced solar power systems to keep your home running day and night. Your system can be sized to your energy needs — from basic lighting and appliances to full off-grid capability with battery backup.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Rooftop solar panels sized to your load</li>
            <li>Lithium battery storage for overnight and cloudy days</li>
            <li>Inverter/charger system for AC power throughout the home</li>
            <li>Compatible with grid tie-in if desired</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="og-card">
          <div class="og-card__icon">&#x1F6BD;</div>
          <h3>Composting Toilets</h3>
          <p>A composting toilet eliminates the need for a sewer connection entirely — ideal for properties without mains sewerage, rural blocks, or fully off-grid setups. Modern composting toilets are odour-free and low-maintenance.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>No plumbing connection required</li>
            <li>Suitable for all climates</li>
            <li>Various models available (electric, non-electric)</li>
            <li>Low water usage — no flush required</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="og-card">
          <div class="og-card__icon">&#x1F4A7;</div>
          <h3>Rainwater Harvesting</h3>
          <p>Capture and store rainwater from your roof for drinking, cooking, and washing. A well-designed rainwater system can provide all the water you need on most Queensland properties.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>First-flush diverter for water quality</li>
            <li>Tank sizing matched to your rainfall and usage</li>
            <li>Pump and filtration system for mains-pressure delivery</li>
            <li>UV or filter purification options for drinking water</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="og-card">
          <div class="og-card__icon">&#x267B;&#xFE0F;</div>
          <h3>Greywater Systems</h3>
          <p>Responsibly manage wastewater from your sinks, shower and laundry with a greywater system. Treated greywater can be used for garden irrigation, reducing your total water footprint.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Greywater diversion and filtration</li>
            <li>Compliant with Queensland greywater regulations</li>
            <li>Suitable for gardens, lawns and irrigation</li>
            <li>Reduces load on blackwater systems</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container og-benefits">
      <p class="eyebrow">Why Go Off-Grid?</p>
      <h2>The Benefits of Independent Living</h2>
      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <div class="benefit">
          <h3>Lower Living Costs</h3>
          <p>Eliminate or significantly reduce electricity, water and sewerage bills. Solar and rainwater pay for themselves over time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
          <h3>Energy Independence</h3>
          <p>No more power outages or price hikes. Generate your own power and store it for when you need it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
          <h3>Location Freedom</h3>
          <p>Park on rural land, a rural block, or a property without mains services — your home works wherever you are.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
          <h3>Reduced Environmental Impact</h3>
          <p>Smaller footprint, renewable energy, water recycling — off-grid living is one of the most sustainable choices you can make.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
          <h3>Resilience</h3>
          <p>Immune to grid failures, water restrictions, and supply disruptions. Your home keeps running no matter what.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
          <h3>Future-Proof Investment</h3>
          <p>As energy and water costs continue to rise, off-grid systems become more valuable every year.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--dark">
    <div class="container og-cta">
      <h2>Interested in Off-Grid Living?</h2>
      <p>Talk to us about designing your off-grid package. We'll help you choose the right systems for your property, climate and budget.</p>
      <div class="og-cta__btns">
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--accent">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="tel:0753158365" class="btn btn--ghost">(07) 5315 8365</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
.page-hero {
  background: var(--color-surface-dark);
  color: #fff;
  padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
}
.page-hero h1 { color: #fff; }
.page-hero__sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,.7); margin-top: .75rem; font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 560px; }

.og-intro h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; max-width: 700px; }
.og-intro p { color: var(--color-text-body); max-width: 760px; }

.og-systems {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: 1.5rem;
  margin-top: 2.5rem;
}
.og-card {
  background: #fff;
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 2rem;
}
.og-card__icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.og-card h3 { margin-bottom: .65rem; }
.og-card > p { color: var(--color-text-body); font-size: .92rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.og-card ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .4rem; }
.og-card ul li {
  font-size: .87rem;
  color: var(--color-text-body);
  padding-left: 1.1rem;
  position: relative;
}
.og-card ul li::before {
  content: '✓';
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  color: var(--color-primary);
  font-weight: 700;
}

.benefits-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1.75rem;
  margin-top: 2.5rem;
}
.benefit h3 { font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: .5rem; }
.benefit p { font-size: .9rem; color: var(--color-text-body); }

.og-cta { text-align: center; }
.og-cta h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
.og-cta p { color: rgba(255,255,255,.7); margin-bottom: 2rem; max-width: 560px; margin-inline: auto; }
.og-cta__btns { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

.btn {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: .9rem 2rem;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background .2s, transform .15s;
  text-align: center;
}
.btn--accent { background: var(--color-accent); color: #fff; }
.btn--accent:hover { opacity: .9; transform: translateY(-2px); }
.btn--ghost { background: transparent; color: #fff; border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.5); }
.btn--ghost:hover { border-color: #fff; }

@media (max-width: 860px) {
  .og-systems { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .benefits-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .benefits-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
